{"tid":1677480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣萬同志遊行　舉彩虹旗撐港人","createTime":"2019-10-27T06:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T11:42:21.000Z","uid":187565,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"513f93575d8fd37b53ecaa655d9edb202321625a","tid":1677480,"uid":187565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2jHR1C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2jHR1C.jpg&h=4c0febcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動熱潮不退，世界各地繼續為港人打氣，台北昨日舉行萬人同志大遊行，不少支持者沿途舉起象徵平權運動的彩虹旗，現場更有人手持支持香港爭民主運動的旗幟，支持者高喊「台灣民主撐同志，台灣同志撐香港」。而在日本東京也有過百支持者戴上習近平面具，為港人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n台灣同志遊行昨午從台北市政府前廣場出發，沿忠孝東路前往終點凱達格蘭大道，遊行路線總長約5.5公里。參加者盛裝打扮出席，有人穿婚紗、扮蜘蛛俠，也有支持者帶「光復香港、時代革命」旗幟參加。主辦單位表示，今年超過20萬人參加。香港民間人權陣線的Figo台上表示，自己很幸運可以參加遊行，呼籲大家守住這個民主、自由的地方，主持人帶領民眾高喊「台灣民主撐同志，台灣同志撐香港」及「反極權，撐同志」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191027/20794702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F20794702&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=e21b137e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F20794702&h=dfa6dc9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191027/20794702</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊做民主鬥士"},{"pid":"b78f617a6fcd1010d2fa9e8ab5c97bc6a32e27ec","tid":1677480,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"9ef83106a7cf020c6bb75fae6ea2eca6ac1324c2","tid":1677480,"uid":187565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:36:42.